          <h3>CONTEXT</h3>
          <p>Arkpad is the first online platform that gathered products and services in the world of Architecture, Interior Design and Decoration with accurate curation in Brazil. An online reference for Designers and Architects that aimed to create a community of professionals and make the experience of design pleasurable and easier through a community platform and marketplace. <a href="https://www.arkpad.com.br/" target="_blank">More about arkpad ></a></p>

